API Documentation

Authentication Router

POST /signup - Sign up a new user.
POST /login - Log in an existing user.
POST /logout - Log out the current user.

Profile Router

GET /profile/view - View the user's profile.

PATCH /profile/edit - Edit the user's profile.

PATCH /profile/password - Update or reset the user's password (Forgot password API).

Connection Request Router

POST /request/send/:status/userID
POST /request/review/accepted/:requestId - Accept a connection request by its ID.

POST /request/review/rejected/:requestId - Reject a connection request by its ID.

User Router

GET /user/connections - Get the list of all connected users.
GET /user/requests - Get the list of connection requests for the current user.
GET /user/feed - Fetch the profiles of other users on the platform.

Status Codes for Connection Requests

ignore

interested

accepted

rejected

